1. Videla sam ogromnu *gromadu* kamenja na vrhu brda. (I saw a huge *pile* of rocks at the top of the hill.)
2. Prošle godine smo imali ogromnu *poplavu* u našem gradu. (Last year we had a massive *flood* in our city.)
3. Ona ima ogromnu *kolekciju* umetničkih slika. (She has a massive *collection* of art paintings.)
4. Za doručak sam pojeo ogromnu *porciju* jaja i slanine. (I had a huge *portion* of eggs and bacon for breakfast.)
5. Videla sam ogromnu *grupu* ljudi ispred pozorišta. (I saw a huge *group* of people in front of the theater.)
6. Stado ovaca je bilo ogromno, imalo je *ogromnu* površinu pašnjaka. (The sheep flock was enormous, it had a *huge* grazing area.)
7. Sinoć sam videla ogromnu *zmiju* u mom dvorištu. (Last night I saw a huge *snake* in my yard.)
8. On je nasledio ogromno *bogatstvo* od svog dede. (He inherited a massive *fortune* from his grandfather.)
9. Moj kauč je ogromna *udobnost* kada se vratim kući. (My couch is a huge *comfort* when I come back home.)
10. Ogromna *iznenađenja* su nas čekala na kraju filma. (Huge *surprises* were waiting for us at the end of the movie.)